the way I thought they were treating me. The ending of this story is when my items , my belongings were removed from my placed without
my knowing and lying that this was done by a marshal who had a court order to do so. When there was no court order to do so. 
The problem that I had in all of this was that I had faith in our City's judicial system that I would be given a fair opportunity 
to go to court and be given legal aid and financial support where it did not come in time or not at all.

When all of this went down when I came back to the States on February 9 2023. I arrived tired and concerned about the situation
that I left the house in. I already knew the situation was not great but with very little help from familiy, friends and city support systems. I was not that shocked by the fact that I was locked out of the apartment. my keys were not working and I notice that there
